---
title: Sweet & Spicy BBQ Bean Burgers with BBQ Caramelized Onion, Pepper Jack, Dill Pickle & Potato Wedges
description: Our chefs are keeping that burger love alive for the vegetarians in the house! These hearty bean burgers are packed with classic BBQ flavor and marbled AND topped with melty pepper jack. They’re pan-fried until crisp on the outside and tender on the inside, then tucked into soft buns slathered with BBQ mayo and topped with sweet caramelized onion and crunchy dill pickle slices. This charmer of a vegetarian dinner idea comes with crispy roasted potato wedges, because we get you, and we heart you.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sweet-spicy-bbq-bean-burgers-8f772a1d.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/sweet-spicy-bbq-bean-burgers-64107f61c10333201c02a6ba-5f30c269.pdf
author: HelloFresh
servings: 2
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/sweet-spicy-bbq-bean-burgers-64107f61c10333201c02a6ba
course: main course
time required: 45 minutes
cuisine: North America
nutrition:
  calories: 1090 kcal
